
一，realsense　sdk 安装
realsense opencv 官方示例：https://github.com/IntelRealSense/librealsense/tree/master/wrappers/opencv
中文博客讲解安装sdk       ：https://blog.csdn.net/z17816876284/article/details/79159518

build步骤:
	mkdir librealsense
	cd librealsense
	cmake .. -DBUILD_EXAMPLES=true
	sudo make
        sudo make install (安装在了/usr/local/bin  /usr/local/include /usr/local/lib)
测试：
　　　　	cd /build/example/capture
    	./rs-capture



二，opencv安装

opencv 3.4 github仓库：https://github.com/opencv/opencv

opencv 源代码构建官网说明：https://docs.opencv.org/trunk/d7/d9f/tutorial_linux_install.html 
(注意：
１．cmake 之前先安装libavresample:  sudo apt-get install libavresample-dev
２．由讨论得到的官方示例：https://community.intel.com/t5/Items-with-no-label/OpenCV-and-D435/td-p/477442)



opencv 源代码构建博客说明: https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38236355/article/details/88864023 


三，示例
官方示例：https://github.com/IntelRealSense/librealsense/tree/master/examples


